last_episode_to_air.name: Umi Rescue Copter
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Team gets a distress call from way out in the ocean. Their friend Danny the Dolphin hurt his tail and can't swim! UmiCar transforms into Umi RescueCopter and the Team sets out to save Danny and fix his tail.

name: Team Umizoomi
overview: They're mini, they're mighty and they're built for math! When someone has a problem in Umi City, Milli, Geo, and Bot use their mighty math powers to help save the day!

episodes.name: The Kite Festival
episodes.overview: When a gust of wind scatters the pieces of Jeannie's kite, the team must search for the pieces to put her kite back together.

episodes.name: The Aquarium Fix-It
episodes.overview: The team is called in to help fix a crack in the seahorse tank at the Umi City Aquarium.

episodes.name: Carnival
episodes.overview: The team must search the Umi City Carnival for Jake's lost stuffed animal.

episodes.name: Picnic
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot must help their friend Anna find her missing lunchbox and thermos before they head out for a picnic.

episodes.name: Super Trip to the Supermarket
episodes.overview: The team must go to the supermarket to collect the items for Tyler's favorite snack.

episodes.name: Subway Heroes
episodes.overview: The team must help when Daniel's father is trapped on a broken subway train.

episodes.name: The Milk Out
episodes.overview: When the farmer gets sick, the team must help fill Umi City's milk order.

episodes.name: The Dinosaur Museum Mishap
episodes.overview: When a thunderstorm frightens the dinosaurs, the team must find them and return them to the museum before the dinosaur show.

episodes.name: The Rolling Toy Parade
episodes.overview: The team must find all the parts of Nick's lion toy before Umi City Park's rolling toy parade.

episodes.name: Special Delivery
episodes.overview: When Anthony forgets to put a stamp on a package for his grandmother, the team heads to the post office to make sure the package is delivered during "Just-Because-I-Love-You Day."

episodes.name: Ready for Take-Off
episodes.overview: When Andy's plane is not able to take off, the team heads to the airport to help.

episodes.name: Ice Cream Truck
episodes.overview: Geo is meeting his friend Dylan so they can go meet the ice cream truck and get some ice cream treats, but when they get to the corner, they find out that the ice cream truck is missing!  Geo meets up with Milli and Bot, and they set out to find the missing truck. Before the day is through, they locate the stranded truck, fix its flat tire and hop inside to make enough ice cream pizzas for Dylan and his friends.  All that’s left is to play the ice cream song to let everyone know the ice cream truck is on the way!

episodes.name: The Wild West Toy Train Show
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot can’t wait to meet their friend Ethan at “The Wild West Toy Train Show,” but before they hop in the Umi Car for their outing, the Umi Alarm sounds.  A big gust of wind has blown Ethan’s ticket out of his hands all the way up to the top of Wild West Mountain!  Poor Ethan can’t get into the Train Show without his ticket, so using their mighty math powers, the Team scales the mountain, rescues the ticket and returns it safely to Ethan.

episodes.name: The Butterfly Dance Show
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi is at their friend Sophia’s school to see her star in the “Butterfly Dance Show.”  (And Milli has a supporting role!)  But when the Umi Alarm sounds, they discover that Sophia’s butterfly costume isn’t finished!  Milli, Geo and Bot navigate the halls of the school to the costume room and using their Mighty Math Powers, they work fast to put the finishing touches on the butterfly costume.  But to get the costume ready in time, they’ll have to find a way to unlock Door Mouse’s supply closet door and find a missing butterfly wing before the “Butterfly Dance Show” begins

episodes.name: The Elephant Sprinkler
episodes.overview: Kayla’s fun at the water playground comes to an abrupt end when the elephant water sprinkler stops working.  To help Kayla, Team Umizoomi needs to know how water gets to Umi City.  “How Does It Work” shows the process and now it’s up to the Team to figure out where the problem is and fix it fast.  The tiny super heroes build a super submarine and zoom through the underground water system to help get the water sprinkler flowing again.

episodes.name: Playground Heroes
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot reward themselves for cleaning up Umi Headquarters with a trip to the playground. But just as they’re getting ready to leave, they get a call on the Umi Alarm from their friend Mia. A storm has left the sandbox, swings, slide, and bouncy bridge in disarray and until everything gets fixed, the park will remain closed. The Umizoomi team tackles the task using mighty math powers and soon the playground is as good as new. The park ranger unlocks the gate and Milli, Geo and Bot join Mia and her friends for some hard-earned playtime.

episodes.name: To The Library
episodes.overview: Olivia is sleeping over at her Grandpa’s house, but she forgot to bring her favorite bedtime story “Goodnight Polka Dot Pirate.”  Milli, Geo and Bot are on the case.  They know a place where you can get any book you need - the Umi City Library!  Umi Car zips them to the scene, where they find out how the library works and even get their very own library card.  With a little tap dancing on the computer’s keyboard, they get the call number of the beloved book and traverse the vast array of bookcases and shelves to find it.  Umi Car meets them at the check out desk, and the team gets the book to Olivia right before bedtime so Grandpa can read her to sleep with her favorite pirate adventure!

episodes.name: Favorite Things Show
episodes.overview: The trio look for their friend's lost shell collection by retracing her steps on an elevator, in a laundry room and through a frog pond. Milli is visiting her friend Emily’s class for Favorite Things Day, the day everyone brings in their favorite things to show the whole class. Emily can’t wait to show the three sparkly shells she found at Sparkle Beach, but when she opens her treasure box, they’re gone! She must have dropped the shells on her way to school! Milli, Geo and Bot rush back to Emily’s apartment building to retrace her steps. Elevator escapades, laundry room adventures, and leaping lily pads over Frog Pond are all in a day’s work for our mighty heroes as they try to find Emily’s sparkle shells in time for the show.

episodes.name: The Big Boat Race
episodes.overview: The team helps Sonya fix her sailboat in time for the boat race.

episodes.name: Race Around Umi City
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi must race around Umi City to win balloons for Sam.

episodes.name: Chicks in the City
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi visits their friend Colin at his school, where six baby chicks have just hatched! But when the baby chicks mistakenly venture out into Umi City, it's up to Team Umizoomi to bring them back safely.

episodes.name: The Ghost Family Costume Party
episodes.overview: The team must help a little ghost solve riddles while on his way to a costume party.

episodes.name: Santa's Little Fixers
episodes.overview: It's Christmas Eve and someone is calling in on the Umi Alarm from far away. It's Santa Claus!

episodes.name: The Great UmiCar Rescue
episodes.overview: The team must rush to save UmiCar when he gets stranded on a far away iceberg.

episodes.name: Purple Monkey Mission
episodes.overview: The team must help the purple monkey find his way to his new home in the Umi City Zoo.

episodes.name: Day at the Museum
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi searches through exhibits at the museum to try to find their friend's missing star tokens.

episodes.name: Super Soap!
episodes.overview: When Silly Bear is covered in glue, the team must deliver some Super Soap to help him get clean.

episodes.name: Counting Comet
episodes.overview: The team must help a comet reach the launch pad of the Umi City rocket ship before it blasts off.

episodes.name: Crazy Skates
episodes.overview: Bot goes out of control when wearing roller skates and Milli and Geo says that wearing the skates makes people go super fast but, there is no way for him to stop.

episodes.name: Milli Saves the Day
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot are having a picnic in the forest. While Bot is picking three apples from an apple tree, he and Geo get stuck in honey. Silly Bear is planning to make a cake, but eventually spots more honey on the ground. He then lifts Geo and Bot, puts them in a jar and takes them to his cave. They have to hurry or else they would be baked in the cake. The only hero who can save them is Milli. She has to go on a solo mission and rescue them before it's too late.

episodes.name: Umi Fire Truck
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi tries to save the day in their Umi fire truck.

episodes.name: Ellee the Elephant
episodes.overview: Ellee the Elephant is sad because she wants to get to the circus, so it's up to Team Umizoomi to help her get through UmiCity to Big Top on time!

episodes.name: Umi Egg Hunt
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi are on an egg-cellent adventure! The gang travels to Rabbit Town to find the missing rainbow egg.

episodes.name: The Legend of the Blue Mermaid
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi tries to rescue The Blue Mermaid from Squiddy the Squid.

episodes.name: Shark Car
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot work together to bring the Shark Car back to a boy who's on a ferry.

episodes.name: Journey To Numberland
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot are going to see the King of Numbers who loves numbers more than anyone else in the world. But Zilch the Wizard imprisons the King in his castle and throws the three keys needed to release the King.

episodes.name: Umi Toy Store
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot are meeting their friend Colin at the Umi City Toy Store.

episodes.name: Buster the Lost Dog
episodes.overview: When a game of fetch goes awry, Anna's dog Buster finds himself stuck in a bucket at the top of a construction site and only Team Umizoomi can save him! But to get there, they'll need to follow the city?s many street signs.

episodes.name: The Incredible Presto
episodes.overview: Oh no! The Incredible Presto gets himself trapped in a giant watermelon! It's up to Milli, Geo, and Bot to use Presto's magic wand to save him in time for his magic show!

episodes.name: Cuckoo Bears
episodes.overview: The Cuckoo Bears are performing in Umi City. But when Team Umizoomi goes to meet them, the wind blows their gears away and they lose the power to play their instruments. It's up to the Team to get the gears back in time for the show.

episodes.name: Stompasaurus
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi's friend Wyatt is excited for his new toy, Stompasaurus, to arrive. But when Stompasaurus' parts fall off the delivery truck, it's up to Milli, Geo and Bot to return the toy's missing parts to their friend.

episodes.name: Job Well Done
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi's friend David is doing chores around his house to earn money for a cool Red Racer Bike. To help David earn the 52 UmiDollars he needs, Milli, Geo, and Bot split up and find jobs to do all around Umi City.

episodes.name: Rainy Day Rescue
episodes.overview: It's a rainy day in Umi City when Casey calls Team Umizoomi with an emergency. A nest full of baby birds has fallen into the flooded street, and now it's floating away. The Team must rescue the baby birds and teach them how to fly away.

episodes.name: Team Umizoomi vs. The Shape Bandit
episodes.overview: The Shape Bandit is creating chaos wherever he goes, but when he steals Geo's Shape Belt, he really crosses the line. Team Umizoomi must square off against furry enemy #1 to save their city and get Geo's Shape Belt back.

episodes.name: Shooting Star!
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi is spending the day at Umi City Ranch. Shooting Star is the smallest horse on the ranch - too small to pull a bale of hay. The team volunteers to seek out the four magic horseshoes that will help Shooting Star grow.

episodes.name: Presto's Magic House
episodes.overview: Presto the Magician calls the team with a big problem: he left his magic wand in the washing machine, and the spinning is making the wand shoot crazy magic! Team Umizoomi will need to use their Mighty Math Powers to save Presto and return his magic wand.

episodes.name: DoorMouse In Space
episodes.overview: When DoorMouse is launched into outer space on a path headed for Mars, it's up to Milli, Geo and Bot to save DoorMouse and return him to Earth. Along the way, the team encounters speeding stars, mysterious aliens and massive meteors.

episodes.name: The Umi Games
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot are getting ready to play in the biggest sports event around: The Umi Games! At the Umi Games, there are four sports-- Soccer, Swimming, Basketball, Biking - and any team who wins all of the games receives a big Sports Trophy! But winning won't be easy. Team Umizoomi will be playing against... Sports Robots! The Sports Robots are programmed to be the fastest, strongest, most agile competitors in Umi City. Milli, Geo and Bot will have to rely on their Mighty Math Powers to outsmart the android athletes and win that trophy!

episodes.name: The Kitty Rescue
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot love their pets, so they know how their friend Jonathan feels when he can't find his kitten, Brownie. Using Bot's Bellyscreen, Team Umizoomi and Jonathan spot Brownie all alone at the bottom of a well! It's up to Team Umizoomi to rescue Brownie, and bring him back to Jonathan.

episodes.name: The Great Shape Race
episodes.overview: UmiCar and DumpTruck are in a race to the top of Shape Mountain to see who will win the big prize... a magic Dodecahedron! But the Team needs to keep an eye on DumpTruck - he'll stop at nothing to win!

episodes.name: Animal School House
episodes.overview: Farmer Dan's animals have roamed away from the farm and found their way inside the Umi City schoolhouse! Can Team Umizoomi catch all the animals before they turn Umi City's schoolhouse into a total zoo?

episodes.name: Doctor Bot
episodes.overview: When the Team's friend Mike falls off his scooter and scrapes his knee, it's Dr. Bot to the rescue! The Team sets off to the playground to deliver a bandage to Mike, while they remedy tricky situations along the way!

episodes.name: Boardwalk Games
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot set out to use their mighty math powers to play games at the boardwalk in order to help their friend win an exciting prize.

episodes.name: Lost and Found Toys
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot help their friend Josie find her missing toy horse in the school's Lost and Found Box. But when they discover three other lost toys left in the box, they're determined to get them back to their owners!

episodes.name: Let's Play Math Dragons
episodes.overview: Team Umizoomi loves Math Dragons because it's unlike any other video game. To play it, the team steps inside the screen and transports themselves into the mystical world of Math Dragons. They take on the exciting quest of conquering the different levels of the game, where they must collect the three baby dragon eggs to win. But the world of Math Dragons is not like Umi City! Milli, Geo and Bot embark on brave adventures with dragons that stomp, chomp and fly their way through medieval passageways and majestic mountains. Can they find all three eggs before it's GAME ...

episodes.name: Haircut Hijinx
episodes.overview: The Team's friend Owen is really excited: he's about to get a haircut! But when Owen's money blows away, the Team sets out on a high-stakes adventure to get it back.

episodes.name: The Umi City Treasure Hunt
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot are being pirates at the Umi City beach when they run into their favorite pirate friend, Squarebeard! Squarebeard gives the Team a treasure map that leads to the long lost treasure of Umi City. To open the treasure, they need to find three keys hidden throughout the city. The team sets off in Pirate Ship UmiCar on a thrilling hunt that takes them through the library, the bank vault and the bell tower.

episodes.name: A Sledding Snow Day
episodes.overview: The Team's friend Sanjay is desperate to go sledding, but there's a problem: he doesn't have a sled! Milli, Geo and Bot must embark on a snowy journey through Umi City to bring a super-sled to Sanjay.

episodes.name: The Boy With the Dragon Skateboard
episodes.overview: In the fourth-season opener, the trio try to reassemble a broken skateboard for their friend.

episodes.name: City of Lost Penguins
episodes.overview: The trio must round up a bunch of lost penguins at the zoo.

episodes.name: UmiCar's Birthday Present
episodes.overview: Today is UmiCar's birthday party and everyone's having a fantastic time. But when The TroubleMakers crash the party and steal UmiCar's birthday present, the chase is on to get the present back.

episodes.name: Robo Tools
episodes.overview: The Team's friend Travis and his mom were on their way to his soccer game when their car got a flat tire. It's up to Team Umizoomi to get to Travis and fix his tire in time for his game. And with Bot's Robo-Tools, they can fix anything.

episodes.name: The Sunshine Fairy
episodes.overview: The Team discovers a secret door to a magical forest. Inside, they meet Sunny the Sunshine Fairy, who has the power of the sun. But when Grog, a jealous gnome, steals her sunshine power, it's up to the Team to help her get it back.

episodes.name: Little Panda Joe
episodes.overview: A baby panda named Little Joe is lost in Umi City! The Team finds him and sets off on a journey to take him back home to his family at the Panda House, taking good care of him all along the way.

episodes.name: Stolen Lunches
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot pursue the TroubleMakers when they steal all of the children's lunch boxes.

episodes.name: Meatball Madness
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo, and Bot must retrieve the red stop button for Chef Mario's Meatball Machine after the TroubleMakers steal the button, allowing it to make too much meatballs and stealing the emergency stop.

episodes.name: Umi Grand Prix
episodes.overview: Shark Car and UmiCar are best car friends, and they're racing together as a team in the Umi Grand Prix, the biggest race in Umi City. However, some of Team Umizoomi's meanest rivals, the Shape Bandit, Dump Truck, Squiddy, and the TroubleMakers are in the big race. Even with help from Milli, Geo, and Bot, can the two best pals win this big race?

episodes.name: Gloopy Fly Home
episodes.overview: When an alien crash-lands in Umi City, the team must help him find the star crystals that make his spaceship fly.

episodes.name: Movie Madness!
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot chase the Troublemakers through the cinema when they steal all of the movie snacks.

episodes.name: Umi Ninjas
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot must use their ninja skills to retrieve their stolen ninja trophy.

episodes.name: UmiCops!
episodes.overview: The chief of police calls the UmiCops to catch the 12 stinkbugs who are on the loose in Umi City.

episodes.name: Umi Knights
episodes.overview: Milli, Geo and Bot are UmiKnights who must save the kingdom by helping a dragon find his glasses.

episodes.name: Lost Fairy Tales in the City
episodes.overview: When Zeppo the Wizard's wand zaps a book of fairy tales, the team must find missing characters from the stories.

episodes.name: Sleeping UmiCar
episodes.overview: The team must find the ingredients for a wake up potion when Zeppo the Wizard's sleeping potion makes UmiCar fall asleep.

episodes.name: Gizmos Gone Wild!
episodes.overview: The team must use their mighty math powers when a group of gizmo robots malfunction and wreak havoc at the Umi City Mall.

episodes.name: Umi Space Heroes
episodes.overview: When the TroubleMakers break the moon into four pieces and scatter around in space, Team Umizoomi have to find the missing pieces of the moon before the TroubleMakers stop them.

episodes.name: Umi Rescue Copter
episodes.overview: The Team gets a distress call from way out in the ocean. Their friend Danny the Dolphin hurt his tail and can't swim! UmiCar transforms into Umi RescueCopter and the Team sets out to save Danny and fix his tail.
